fg_segments: Privacy Policy This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which 4K Download Applications collect, use, maintain and disclose information collected from users ("User").
1. PERSONAL INFORMATION. 4K Download Applications don't collect, store or analyse the user personal information or the information about his downloaded content.
4K Download Applications are enabled to receive the following information from User's computer: the facts of program launch, termination, crashes or other events related to the downloading process.
2. USAGE. 4K Download Applications should only be used to download videos, audio or images you own or have the copyright to.
If you do not have this permission please contact the video owner.
The user takes all responsibility for this app usage, Open Media LLC is not responsible for the users actions whilst using the app.
3. YOUR ACCEPTANCE OF THESE TERMS. By using this app, you signify your acceptance of this policy.
If you do not agree to this policy, please do not use our app.
Your continued use of the app following the posting of changes to this policy will be deemed your acceptance of those changes.
4. CONTACTING US. If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, the practices of apps, or your dealings with apps, please contact us at support@4kdownload.com.
